name: You Don't Mezz with Zigator Z
description:
Digital collage that made on December 14, 2021.


A tribute to Mahendra Nazar's Zigator Z, a very cool character.


Main Images from rijksmuseum.nl, and the rest from other sites on the internet.

Portrait of Gerard Andriesz Bicker. Creator: Bartholomeus van der Helst. Date: 1642.

Friedrich Christian (1722-63), Elector of Saxony and King of Poland. Creator: Gottfried Boy. Date: 1751.
